{"pageProps":{"problem":{"id":"t5-train-3","grade":"7","semester":"up","category":"有理数","title":"针对训练3：数轴上的距离问题","difficulty":4,"tags":["数轴","距离","绝对值"],"content":"数轴上 $A$、$B$、$C$ 三点表示的数分别为 $a$、$b$、$c$，且满足 $|a + 5| + |b - 3| + |c - 1|^2 = 0$。求 $|a - b| + |b - c|$ 的值。","steps":[{"title":"求 a、b、c 的值","content":"因为 $|a + 5| \\geq 0$，$|b - 3| \\geq 0$，$|c - 1|^2 \\geq 0$\n\n且它们的和为 $0$\n\n所以 $a + 5 = 0$，$b - 3 = 0$，$c - 1 = 0$\n\n即 $a = -5$，$b = 3$，$c = 1$","formula":"a = -5, b = 3, c = 1"},{"title":"计算距离和","content":"$|a - b| = |-5 - 3| = 8$\n\n$|b - c| = |3 - 1| = 2$\n\n$|a - b| + |b - c| = 8 + 2 = 10$","formula":"10"}]},"id":"t5-train-3"},"__N_SSG":true}